{"tid":262279,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Bitcoin下挫後反彈  九流廢老「經濟學家」關焯照：持續發展必須政府監管","createTime":"2017-05-29T05:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T02:49:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cab5e4b2dff462356efb2003f052ab5a4748cf17","tid":262279,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Bitcoin新高後下挫再反彈  九流廢老「經濟學家」關焯照：持續發展必須政府監管</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170526/large/1495793309_757f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170526%2Flarge%2F1495793309_757f.jpg&h=1e1eaecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】虛擬貨幣Bitcoin價格走勢如坐過山車，前日急跌兩成後，昨一度重返2,600美元樓上。有學者認為，虛擬貨幣近日炒風熾熱，反映市場投機者想短炒獲利，非看好虛擬貨幣前景。<br />\n<br />\n科技網站Tech crunch指Bitcoin價格波動，主因全球最大虛擬貨幣交易平台Coinbase 因巨大流量「死機」，暫停運作數小時。彭博追蹤Bitcoin價格數據指，Bitcoin周四曾升見2,798.97美元新高，本港凌晨約1時半跌至2,234.97美元，跌幅達564美元。<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin昨一度回升至2664.91美元。截至本港昨晚約8時，Bitcoin報2581.18美元。<br />\n<br />\n經濟學家關焯照指現階段買Bitcoin多數屬投機、風險大和博短暫獲利，非押注Bitcoin發展成具交易能力的虛擬貨幣。關提出若要Bitcoin持續發展，政府須介入監管及規管交易平台。<br />\n<br />\n對虛擬貨幣近日被瘋狂炒作，經濟學家關焯照認為：「啲人貪婪，個市升得快，總知喺爆破之前，我賺到就得喇！」<br />\n<br />\n關焯照指Bitcoin是一個好假的市場，市場投機氣氛重，大家才瘋炒Bitcoin。他續指現階段買Bitcoin都是投機性質、風險又大及搏短暫，並非長線看好Bitcoin發展成為有交易能力的虛擬貨幣，Bitcoin亦沒有財富儲存能力。<br />\n<br />\n關焯照又指出虛擬貨幣的交易平台欠監管，「最擔心入面嘅Bitcoin全部走哂佬，即係被Hacked哂，咁點算，邊個賠呀? 所以，Bitcoin不會維持（sustain）得耐，除非政府介入監管。」<br />\n<br />\n若要Bitcoin成為一種貨幣，關焯照指需要有政府支持或中央銀行發行。另外，市場視Bitcoin作為商品也不太恰當。關焯照提到金、銀和銅等商品均擁有本身價值，但Bitcoin只屬虛擬貨幣，其價值是接觸不到，跟傳統金幣、銅或紙幣不同；紙幣是由政府確定的法定貨幣，Bitcoin仍不未取得政府法定地位。<br />\n<br />\nBILL GATES：NOBODY CAN STOP BITCOIN<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k0HmrSfJwhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk0HmrSfJwhU&d=hRaJm2Xb%2FvLoA%2B8uTLsYNB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=81897b66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k0HmrSfJwhU</a>"},{"pid":"8313f9565108ce7479774430f549160bcfe6cc92","tid":262279,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cb5347c5806242e4080b39bd80f25a615e7ba36","tid":262279,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"有政府支持就完反撚本身存在意義，明唔明架佢"},{"pid":"1283c2d1d55d920027e403ec58ff1b27745239ea","tid":262279,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"經濟學家喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c9a1d481cc852edb240cfd90d3260aa51cae10","tid":262279,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5311400c23754040b742a7b8824d7c679eafd292","tid":262279,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經濟學家喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢連BTC點運作都未識, 竟然叫「專家」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4dc0371727d33861b618423a5fdd25e74bfc06","tid":262279,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有政府支持就完反撚本身存在意義，明唔明架佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n政府發行的貨幣：隨時狂印！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.financesonline.com/uploads/press.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.financesonline.com%2Fuploads%2Fpress.jpg&h=a79979dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"181cbdd5cb2b63bc975c35937c80d8565f3f8bbd","tid":262279,"uid":33477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:10:31.000Z","msg":"畀政府管BTC 價值跌九成都似"},{"pid":"536cbe9cc795032ff43e267881f749e428182491","tid":262279,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲咁嘅人<br />\n仲帶住副金絲眼鏡</bl