br />\n咪咁快放呀<br />\n唔係長升長有咩<br />\n唔好信d 19經濟學家講嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24da0b724e29026cdd335abfc3908010833e3a34","tid":262279,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"條友識唔識咩叫bitcoin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n專家食屎啦"},{"pid":"2817ea3a28f8863f4aecbc4806816596433fa09d","tid":262279,"uid":105658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>政府何以點監管?法律上?技術上?<br />\n<br />\n經濟學家有冇具體例子?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一個資本主義自由經濟既「經濟學家主張政府干預自由市場<br />\n<br />\n本身已經係反智, <br />\n<br />\n唔撚知佢D乜野經濟學理論</blockquote><br />\n你咪on 9好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢講到好vague, 我唔知佢propose個d措施係監管定係干預<br />\n不過支持自由經濟同支持監管係無衝突<br />\n<br />\nAl Roth:<br />\nI think a useful way to think about free markets is that a free market is a<br />\nmarket with rules and institutions that let it operate freely. When we talk about<br />\na wheel that can rotate freely, we don&rsquo;t mean a wheel that is unconnected to<br />\nanything else. We mean a wheel that has an axle, and well-oiled bearings. I think<br />\nthat is a good metaphor for a free market. A free market needs institutions that<br />\nlet it work well. Markets like the New York Stock Exchange have lots of rules&mdash;<br />\nthey&rsquo;re not laissez-faire markets, they have rules about when they open in the<br />\nmorning, and when they close in the afternoon, and these help keep the market<br />\nthick. And they have rules that have the force of law, like rules against insider<br />\ntrading that you can go to jail for violating, and those rules are intended to make<br />\nit safe for ordinary investors to participate in the market."},{"pid":"307e1c1074d013abefa80f4ec875c0190b837090","tid":262279,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"經濟學家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個學位幾錢呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ff7903caa24ca50603252187285e359160b775","tid":262279,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好講咁多<br />\n樓主快d入返幾手bitcoin啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高位放左大部份<br />\n剩返 0.69XX 個BTC<br />\n<br />\n有乜可以幫到你？</blockquote><br />\n咪咁快放呀<br />\n唔係長升長有咩<br />\n唔好信d 19經濟學家講嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n低D再入<br />\n<br />\n食多幾個浪  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7caf8c2d7b56b432bf0d1c0962ce0a5118bb7f2e","tid":262279,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>政府何以點監管?法律上?技術上?<br />\n<br />\n經濟學家有冇具體例子?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一個資本主義自由經濟既「經濟學家」主張政府干預自由市場<br />\n<br />\n本身已經係反智, <br />\n<br />\n唔撚知佢D乜野經濟學理論</blockquote><br />\nnonononono 政府干預同自由市場有關係 但係你唔能夠話因為政府又干預所以依個市場唔自由<br />\n今時今日所有自由市場都有政府干預 你要諗 干預唔係等於入市 純粹設定規則防止大戶壟斷同樣係干預"},{"pid":"614bb69c88afd2ebacbadc22edb4e7f04af65fce","tid":262279,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好講咁多<br />\n樓主快d入返幾手bitcoin啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高位放左大部份<br